'''Françoise Ellong''' (wavutse 8 Gashyantare 1988) ni umuyobozi wa firime n'umwanditsi wa filimi muri [[Kameruni]]<ref>http://www.africine.org/personne/francoise-ellong-gomez/30098</ref>.

== Ubuzima ==
Ellong yavukiye Douala, muri [[Kameruni]] mu 1988. Afite imyaka 11, yimukiye i Brunoy kubana na nyirarume, maze yandika inkuru ye ya mbere<ref>https://frauenfilmfest.com/en/movie/buried/</ref>. Ellong yitabiriye amarushanwa y'abanditsi bato bavuga [[igifaransa]] mu 2002. Kubera amarushanwa, yagize ubushake bwo kwandika amashusho<ref>https://www.filme-aus-afrika.de/EN/film-database/persons/personen-details/w/3572/</ref>. 

Mu 2006, filime ye ya mbere ngufi, ''Les Colocs'', yarasohotse. Ellong yayoboye filime ye ya mbere yerekana, ''WAKA'', mu 2013<ref>https://www.allocine.fr/personne/fichepersonne_gen_cpersonne=756831.html</ref>. yanditswe na Séraphin Kakouang, bishingiye ku nkuru y'umwimerere ya Ellong<ref>http://deptfordcinema.org/podcast-episodes/ep9</ref>. ''WAKA'' yahawe igihembo cyihariye cy’abacamanza mu iserukiramuco du Cinéma Africain de Khouribga, ndetse n’igihembo cya Dikalo mu iserukiramuco rya Pan-African Cannes<ref>http://africanwomenincinema.blogspot.com/2021/11/tv5monde-afrique-francoise-ellong-enterres.html</ref>.  Yerekanwe mugutangira ibirori bya Ecrans Noirs. Filime ye ya kabiri yerekana, ''Buried'', yasohotse muri 2020<ref>https://www.telerama.fr/cinema/films/w-a-k-a,503970.php</ref>. Nibijyanye no guhura kwinshuti zo mu bwana numukino wagaragaje amabanga.  Ifata amashusho mu mudugudu wa Nkassomo, yatewe inkunga na raporo yamakuru yabonye kuri tereviziyo.<ref>http://www.scenarioaulongcourt.com/Francoise-ELLONG</ref> 

Usibye kwandika no kuyobora, Ellong yasohoye igitabo "Journal Intime d'Un Meurtrier" mu 2008.  Muri 2016, yatangije blog "Le Film Camerounais", bituma ibihembo bya LFC<ref>http://www.ifcameroun.com/douala/evenement-retrospective-francoise-ellong/</ref>.  Ellong yasabye ko hajyaho inkambi z’abakinnyi ba Thierry Ntamack mu 2020, Ntamack amaze kuvuga ko 10 ku ijana gusa by’abakinnyi ba [[Kameruni]] ari beza.<ref>https://www.elle.ci/tag/francoise-ellong/</ref> 

